::KitKat::

She falls from the hit and drops Land Mine. "YOU HONORLESS FREAKS OF 
A MAXIMAL! HONOR IS ABOVE ALL!"  She got up and grabbed her gun. She 
aimed at Deemos and fired, aiming for his head. "I SAID NO MORE 
FIGHTING!  I MEANT IT.  I am a pred of my word.  And I will keep it. 
But if you want a fight, you will have one!"  She transformed into 
wolf mode and went after Deemos.  She tried to bite his face.
